    "name": "update-merge: content-only update preserves every unset field",
    "description": "The merge-safe update GETs the current todo, overlays only the explicitly-set fields, and PUTs the full representation back to the canonical flat route. A content-only update must carry over description, dates, assignees (mapped Person → assignee_ids), and completion subscribers, and must not send notify.",
